data.title: Baptist Medical Center Downtown Office
data.meta_description: Welcome to our Baptist Downtown office, it is conveniently located in the Baptist Medical Centers Pavillion Physicians Office Building. Enter through the "Main Hospital Entrance".
data.text:
Welcome to our Baptist Downtown office, it is conveniently located in the Baptist Medical Centers Pavillion Physicians Office Building. Enter through the "Main Hospital Entrance".

Parking: head toward the ER on Prudential Dr. The Pavilion building will be on the left-hand side before the Weaver (Wolfson's) building and ER. Turn left onto Palm Ave then left again into the parking garage (Palm Ave is in between the garage and Pavilion building). Garage address: 1051 Palm Ave.
